Video clips from the first flight of the new Airbus A380 yesterday (27/4). I was searching the net for some "downloadable" clips of the historic event. I noticed that none was published on Piratebay so I decided to share the ones I found. The first two was posted on the forum at airliners.net by someone calling himself BMIFlyer and the last one was found at a340.net.

The clips are of mediocre quality so if you've got better ones, please share them with us other aviation nuts. ;P

Enjoy!
